        <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-xs shrink-0 shadow-md mt-1" style="background: var(--gradient-btn);">
          E
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1 space-y-2 max-w-[80%]">
          <div class="bg-black/40 backdrop-blur-xl border border-white/10 px-6 py-5 rounded-2xl rounded-tl-none text-sm text-gray-200 leading-relaxed shadow-lg space-y-4">
            
            <p class="font-medium text-white text-base" style="font-family: var(--font-obli);">
              ¡Hola! Puedes mitigar el impacto económico de tus infracciones mediante tres vías legales vigentes:
